== Build Documentation ==
=== Dependencies ===
==== Linux (Debian) ====
* build-essential
* ant
* subversion
* libgtk2.0-dev
* libglib1.2-dev
* libidl-dev
* libxt-dev
* zip
* unzip
* fakeroot
* dpkg-deb
* a Java JDK for ant (java-gcj-compat-dev, sun-java6-jdk, openjdk-6-jdk,...)

==== Windows ====
See http://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Windows_Build_Prerequisites

=== Get build scripts/packager ===
==== Read only / through SVN protocol (TCP port 3690) ====
 $ svn co svn://svn.adullact.net/svnroot/milimail/trunk/packager milimail

==== Read-write / through SSH (TCP port 22) ====
 $ svn co svn+ssh://my_username@svn.adullact.net/svnroot/milimail/trunk/packager milimail
   (replace my_username by your Adullact SSH username)

  // Copy the file server.properties.template to server.properties
 $ cp milimail/server.properties.template milimail/server.properties

  // Set your SSH username in server.properties
 $ sed -i s/SSH_USERNAME/my_username/ milimail/server.properties
   (replace my_username by your Adullact SSH username)

=== Building ===
 $ cd milimail

  // Build and package milimail and extensions
 $ ant build-all

  // OR: build and package milimail
 $ ant extract-milimail update-milimail build-milimail package-milimail
  // OR: build and package extensions
 $ ant package-extensions
